<p>A <code>TreeListItem</code> is an <code>&lt;li role="treeitem"&gt;</code>.
  It can carry <code>aria-expanded</code> (for branches) and
  <code>aria-selected</code> (for the active item).</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/tree-nav/">Tree Nav demo</a>
  for a composed example.</p>
